'''''Bra böckers lexikon''''' ('''''BBL''''') is a [[Swedish language|Swedish]] [[encyclopedia]] published between 1973 and 1996, in four editions with 25 volumes each. The first three editions sold more than 400,000 copies.<ref name=ne>{{cite encyclopedia |encyclopedia=[[Nationalencyklopedin]] |title=''Bra Böckers Lexikon'' |url=http://www.ne.se/bra-b%C3%B6ckers-lexikon |accessdate=2009-07-21 |language=Swedish}}</ref> The first edition was published between 1973–81, the second 1974-82, the third 1983-90 and the fourth 1991-96.  Between 1995-99 a special edition, ''Bra böckers lexikon 2000'', was published.{{fact|date=February 2016}}

